  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing (Food Packaging)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Consultant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Depot Road</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon-Fri: 8.30am-6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic $2,800 - $3,500 + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle customer enquiries and orders.</li><li>Source new sales accounts.</li><li>Identify and develop new sales accounts to drive continuous growth.</li><li>Provide after-sales support to customers.</li><li>Maintain customer relationships through site visits.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of sales experience.</li><li>Friendly and approachable.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80014 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
